{"tid":47574,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"太陽能路燈　入夜沒太陽時竟「休眠」","createTime":"2016-12-20T12:13:54.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-20T15:16:06.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"89b58155c09065e1a944e8898c88c8e48c8e68b8","tid":47574,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T12:13:54.000Z","msg":"2016年12月06日22:30 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20161206/640_40ceb15dad6db26007a3d40199096b92.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20161206%2F640_40ceb15dad6db26007a3d40199096b92.jpg&h=04ecdb11&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n新榮公園附近一整排太陽能路燈，在晚上都沒會亮。黃任膺攝 <br />\n<br />\n太陽能路燈晚上不會亮？台中南區新榮公園周邊，因為有大型的戰車裝置，以及鄰近國立公共資訊圖書館，近來發展為熱門的拍照遊憩去處。不過民眾卻發現有些區域的路燈入夜後根本不會亮，仔細趨近一看，上方還附有太陽能板陳小姐說，看起來比一般路燈更現代科技化，可惜，樹立了一整排都不會亮。附近的民眾都在笑說，因為是太陽能路燈，要白天吸收了太陽能才會亮，晚上就不會亮了！ <br />\n<br />\n投訴人表示，曾試著洽詢市府此事，先打去建設局，公園管理科說是景觀科在管，景觀科說是區公所，南區公所又說是教育局，搞得大家霧沙沙，到最後也問不出所以然。 <br />\n<br />\n南區公所農業及建設科科長張信鴻說，路燈設置地點是文小三十八綠美化的範圍，由教育局委託信義國小代管。被詢及路燈晚上會亮嗎？他表示，因為晚上不會去，因此不清楚。 <br />\n<br />\n教育局主祕鄧進權表示，該區設置太陽能路燈十四盞，應該是會亮，不知是否因日前的天雨等因素故障，將派員檢修，好讓其恢復夜間照明的功能，不致於讓民眾誤會。（黃任膺／台中報導） <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20161206/420_e7faf3ae78e3695396d96bee23fe014c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20161206%2F420_e7faf3ae78e3695396d96bee23fe014c.jpg&h=76f5a316&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n新榮公園附近一整排太陽能路燈，在晚上都沒會亮。黃任膺攝 <br />\n<br />\nlink:<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20161206/1005623/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fnew%2F20161206%2F1005623%2F&d=5HpZ%2FrAUh5jvjgaTu3OudgT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=fa2f4a77\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20161206/1005623/</a>"},{"pid":"715893189c7fff410a73021841b48e169043d9dd","tid":47574,"uid":34742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T12:16:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"59397f7fdaaf249a89f532db1a4686a4e42db65c","tid":47574,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T12:17:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b870a84dc061ab2f7e1b66117a71a27c3e569d0e","tid":47574,"uid":60655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T12:18:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/bl0k3w1i\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fbl0k3w1i&h=c1f61ec7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4f96d4f398e1117c90d196b2e7906b3ba688dd35","tid":47574,"uid":27458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T12:18:22.000Z","msg":"絕對唔會著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf1e2cad04deeae40d11d464684d18da71709e6b","tid":47574,"uid":33463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T12:19:32.000Z","msg":"無太陽果時絕對唔會著<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b60b191e7b97a89bfc946c9d6b2b8819de9aaf3e","tid":47574,"uid":22313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T12:22:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無太陽果時絕對唔會著<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不錯（普通話）"},{"pid":"7254cf5bc439d15bf941b7c063d675328ef92878","tid":47574,"uid":16567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T13:02:34.000Z","msg":"太陽能儲電"},{"pid":"cfddc7bb1016b049a70ea73c1e223719d6fe02a8","tid":47574,"uid":42909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T13:36:24.000Z","msg":"咁有無可能無太陽都會著呢？"},{"pid":"85413410050d43005083af9392251e2b247f878d","tid":47574,"uid":16777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T13:40:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁有無可能無太陽都會著呢？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n用另一枝路燈照住"},{"pid":"33